ment in a specific lab discipline performing high complexity testing in blood banking, chemistry, hematology, microbiology, immunology and clinical microscopy (categorical or generalist certification required). Education/training PREFERRED: Master's Degree in Clinical Lab Science (MSCLS) from an accredited program. Job Type: Full-time Experience: MT: 4 years (Required) Supervisory or Lead or Sr: 3 years (Required) Education: Bachelor's (Required) License: ASCP (Required) Work Location: One location Schedule: Monday to Friday Day shift 8 hour shift Company's website: www.vcuhealth.org "
